---
title: Grilled Surf and Steak Dinner with Foil-Pouch Potatoes and Tarragon Butter
description: This surf and turf dish is simple, saucy and crispy! BBQ steaks, tender potatoes and garlic shrimp are cooked to perfection and topped with a steakhouse-style butter starring tarragon and parsley.
